{"article_id":"yZ4MGs7SWjSTucEo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Iran warned Thursday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that an `` all-out war \" could break out","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"if any country attacks it","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"following weekend bombings of Saudi Arabia ' s oil facilities","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"that the U.S. believes","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Tehran orchestrated .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif ' s stark message to CNN comes a day after U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo tweeted","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"that the \" Iranian regime 's threatening behavior will not be tolerated .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"'' `` I am making a very serious statement","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that we do n't want to engage in a military confrontation , ''","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Zarif said in an interview with the channel .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"`` But we wo n't blink to defend our territory . ''","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"SAUDI OIL ATTACKS ARE AN 'ACT OF WAR ' BY IRAN ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"POMPEO SAYS","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"When asked what would be the consequence of a U.S. or Saudi strike ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Zarif said :","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` All-out war . ''","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"who arrived in the United Arab Emirates on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"America is always pushing for a peaceful resolution .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"America 's top diplomat met earlier Thursday with Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman in Jeddah over Saturday 's attack on a crucial oil processing facility and oil field ,","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"which halved the kingdom 's oil production .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Yemen 's Iranian-backed Houthi rebels have claimed the attack ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"but the U.S. alleges","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Iran carried out the assault .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` The U.S. stands with # SaudiArabia","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and supports its right","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to defend itself , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Pompeo tweeted Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"TRUMP , IN WAKE OF SAUDI OIL ATTACK , SAYS","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"' I DO N'T WANT WAR WITH ANYBODY '","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"speaking from Jeddah , Saudi Arabia , on Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"added","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"even if the `` fraudulent claims '' of responsibility by the Yemen Houthi rebels were true ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` it does n't change the fingerprints of the","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"[ Iran Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei ]","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"as having put at risk the global energy supply . ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Pompeo 's remarks in Saudi Arabia also came hours after President Trump tweeted","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that he had ordered Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin to \" substantially increase sanctions \" on Iran , amid escalating tensions between the two countries .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"Earlier this week , Trump said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"it was `` looking like '' Iran was responsible for the bombing","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"but did not publicly accuse Tehran of the attack .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" Well , it ' s looking that way , \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the president told reporters at the White House on Monday","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"when asked","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"if Iran was responsible .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" We ' ll let you know definitively. \"","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He added :","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" That ' s being checked out right now . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"At a press conference Wednesday , the Saudis displayed broken and burned drones and pieces of a cruise missile","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"that military spokesman Col. Turki Al-Malki identified as Iranian weapons","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"collected after the attack .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"He also played surveillance video","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"showed a drone","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"coming in from the north .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Yemen is to the south of Saudi Arabia .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Eighteen drones and seven cruise missiles were launched in the assault ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Al-Malki said ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"with three missiles failing to make their targets .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"the cruise missiles had a range of 435 miles ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"meaning they could not have been fired from inside Yemen .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"That opinion was shared by weapons experts","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"who spoke to The Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"`` This is the kind of weapon","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"the Iranian regime and the Iranian IRGC are using against the civilian object and facilities infrastructure , ''","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Al-Malki said ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"referring to Iran 's Revolutionary Guards .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"He added :","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` This attack did not originate from Yemen ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"despite Iran 's best effort","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"to make it appear so . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":88,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":82,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":79,"right":81,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":78,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity"